{subhead}Image FX 4.5 Released{def}
{left}
{pp}
Nova Design has released the latest version of the image processing program - Image FX,
with more new features.
{pp}
Image FX 4.5 now comes with even more DrawModes will a new range  compositing tools to
allow you to composite brushes into your images with all the same tools that the
composite tool offers you for full image compositing.
{pp}
New Animation features include KeyFrame Manager to combine images, animations and anim
brushes into one animation. You can also control the path of the animation with different
point methods. You can also scale, stretch or squash and even make 3D type animations
such as flying logos.
{pp}
Upgrades cost as low as $49.95 for existing ImageFX owners, or $279.95 for full version.
Other upgrade or corssgrade options are available.
{pp}
Nova Design, Inc., 1910 Byrd Avenue, Suite 204, Richmond, VA 23230
{pp}
 
